author: rooneg
msg: (import_dir): move the svn:ignores check before the if (dir) else if (file)
logic, since we might as well check it for directories as well as files.
this lets you import a cvs working copy without bringing in the CVS
subdirectories by adding CVS to your global-ignores config option.
